    Page: 150
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Faith
---
Faith is a rare flower of inestimable value. It must be cultivated in the
garden of your heart. It must be watered daily with the water of sincerity.
The weeds of doubts and misgivings should be totally eradicated. Then faith
will strike deep root, blossom and bear the fruit of devotion quickly.
